{"tid":2326034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★武漢肺炎effect----有商人準備自殺","createTime":"2020-12-15T04:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T05:21:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd1b853c838bfda7e83e266d9eb4691f28f5161","tid":2326034,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:34:11.000Z","msg":"在法國巴黎，數以千計酒店東主以及從事婚禮統籌及活動策劃的人士聚集示威，有人更出動「棺材」模型，諷刺當局視他們為非必要行業，沒有在財政上充份支援他們度過新冠肺炎疫情帶來的難關。  原定於明年6月舉行的巴黎航空展要取消，預料業界進一步受創。有示威者指<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>有商人準備自殺</strong></span>，他們會將這些自殺個案納入新冠肺炎死亡宗數內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5fd80afe335d19521e13508b/臨近聖誕歐洲多國收緊防疫限制-荷蘭有示威不滿封鎖措施\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5fd80afe335d19521e13508b%2F%E8%87%A8%E8%BF%91%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%B6%E7%B7%8A%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6-%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E6%9C%89%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=bc464cd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5fd80afe335d19521e13508b/臨近聖誕歐洲多國收緊防疫限制-荷蘭有示威不滿封鎖措施</a>"},{"pid":"38ca7de787fc7a0416e169a05c3b80b8dfe34f20","tid":2326034,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"又中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZdx6DV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZdx6DV.jpg&h=68568ed0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf5e5a370d0c5c6a1968d9c89658462314a51321","tid":2326034,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a632926664d6b54a8e436b5445f8c09f8a7201","tid":2326034,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"believe 中國疫苗"},{"pid":"526e759b4ff78a190e127ccd8a846a3c6f4eab0a",